{"tid":1550281,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我認為我地場革命完咗","createTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:05:28.000Z","uid":57914,"like":14,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f7ca37c31bf887f896c8b8fe02a5e9567da36d","tid":1550281,"uid":57914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:37.000Z","msg":"沙田現場手足冇人上前救<br />\n係呀, 我係冷氣軍師<br />\n大家一齊唔好救, 次次都拉幾十個, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">下個到你</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571b5fb1eda4055deddeb4900482fce6e8c20296","tid":1550281,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我警告你班仆街！<br />\n<br />\n聽日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該幫手執！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企！<br />\n</span></div></span><br />\n<br />\n第二樣野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住為美國風災祈禱：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「多里安」Dorian <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在美國造成最少4人死亡</span></span>，南、北卡州超過35萬戶停電。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=f148ca5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479270-20190907.htm&h=d997d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479270-20190907.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://cbsnews1.cbsistatic.com/hub/i/r/2019/09/05/b6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04/thumbnail/620x349/8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4/0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcbsnews1.cbsistatic.com%2Fhub%2Fi%2Fr%2F2019%2F09%2F05%2Fb6e68e9e-cf87-4f4c-ab1d-437c624fde04%2Fthumbnail%2F620x349%2F8be72af29e5199fec55ab9a6fe7f51a4%2F0905-ctm-dorianbahamas-begnaud-1927196-640x360.jpg&h=6aa446ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國歌(快d聽熟！) 、揮<span style=\"color: red;\">美</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國</span>國旗！！！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC0x5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=37838d35\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"c848fae47c2752077764a5f377a49e6d9dc4831f","tid":1550281,"uid":287755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:08.000Z","msg":"終極反送中英文年鑑上線了(整合9/6-4/9所有事件)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1549878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1549878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"02f07b34a8b4cc6a035c6f68f8e50ef9f7c04803","tid":1550281,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7b08efa57dba708a7a9323bae3ddb347eb2c8cf","tid":1550281,"uid":284630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"現場有人嘗試救, 但係咁岩有度門, 班狗入左去檔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22df84217024f84aaacd9107e9a6508d58da358","tid":1550281,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:27:28.000Z","msg":"唔係阿姐出手先都冇人咁開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7b2df130742d8fe321b56e77265ee81e40b2af","tid":1550281,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T15:27:34.000Z","msg":"好驚下次無人救我，我有犧牲覺悟頭先睇live心談<img src=\"/a